:16,"score":88},{"id":"RAW_13890a03","title":"60%用户还在乱养虾！9 位大神亮招：OpenClaw AI Agent 实战指南","link":"https://www.qbitai.com/2026/03/393244.html","date":"2026-03-30 03:49:08","archive_path":"data/articles/2026/03/RAW_13890a03.json","topicTag":"ai-llm","category":"Artificial_Intelligence","sourceName":"量子位","resourceType":"ARTICLE","readTime":19,"score":87},{"id":"RAW_64321a11","title":"DeepSeek 网页版大升级！随后宕机 11 小时崩上热搜，新模型真的来了","link":"https://www.qbitai.com/2026/03/393235.html","date":"2026-03-30 03:33:58","archive_path":"data/articles/2026/03/RAW_64321a11.json","topicTag":"ai-llm","category":"Artificial_Intelligence","sourceName":"量子位","resourceType":"ARTICLE","readTime":3,"score":86},{"id":"RAW_788348f8","title":"龙虾安全被 3 层硬核架构焊死了！一份面向开发者的硬核生存指南","link":"https://www.qbitai.com/2026/03/393226.html","date":"2026-03-30 02:27:30","archive_path":"data/articles/2026/03/RAW_788348f8.json","topicTag":"ai-llm","category":"Artificial_Intelligence","sourceName":"量子位","resourceType":"ARTICLE","readTime":23,"score":88},{"id":"RAW_c34d5202","title":"发布：llm-mrchatterbox 0.1","link":"https://simonwillison.net/2026/Mar/30/llm-mrchatterbox-2/#atom-everything","date":"2026-03-30 02:20:46","archive_path":"data/articles/2026/03/RAW_c34d5202.json","topicTag":"ai-llm","category":"Artificial_Intelligence","sourceName":"Simon Willison's Weblog","resourceType":"ARTICLE","readTime":1,"score":82},{"id":"RAW_08a954fd","title":"Echo：预测智能的一小步，通往通用智能的一大步","link":"https://mp.weixin.qq.com/s?__biz=MzA3MzI4MjgzMw==&mid=2651024564&idx=1&sn=6fb075d1ca107111ac46eeb2215716fd","date":"2026-03-30 01:34:00","archive_path":"data/articles/2026/03/RAW_08a954fd.json","topicTag":"ai-llm","category":"Artificial_Intelligence","sourceName":"机器之心","resourceType":"ARTICLE","readTime":16,"score":86},{"id":"RAW_32ed6943","title":"ICLR 2026 | 让多模态模型学会主动说话：主动交互从训练到评估的完整方案","link":"https://mp.weixin.qq.com/s?__biz=MzA3MzI4MjgzMw==&mid=2651024564&idx=2&sn=35264986836dd290aa3618d110aaeb85","date":"2026-03-30 01:34:00","archive_path":"data/articles/2026/03/RAW_32ed6943.json","topicTag":"other","category":"Artificial_Intelligence","sourceName":"机器之心","resourceType":"ARTICLE","readTime":18,"score":89},{"id":"RAW_efc1c96f","title":"单张显卡跑出 15 倍推理速度，aiX-apply-4B 小模型加速企业 AI 研发落地","link":"https://www.qbitai.com/2026/03/392787.html","date":"2026-03-30 00:41:45","archive_path":"data/articles/2026/03/RAW_efc1c96f.json","topicTag":"ai-llm","category":"Artificial_Intelligence","sourceName":"量子位","resourceType":"ARTICLE","readTime":8,"score":87},{"id":"RAW_2f0ae428","title":"一周 1300 多个 PR，揭秘 Stripe 内部 AI 工程最佳实践","link":"https://mp.weixin.qq.com/s?__biz=Mzg3NDc2MjQxMg==&mid=2247494116&idx=1&sn=1a3927f31d3cac416fcd74acdfb2e6fc","date":"2026-03-30 00:38:00","archive_path":"data/articles/2026/03/RAW_2f0ae428.json","topicTag":"ai-llm","category":"Artificial_Intelligence","sourceName":"深思圈","resourceType":"ARTICLE","readTime":29,"score":89},{"id":"RAW_67829792","title":"Harness Engineering 来了，SDD 还有意义吗？","link":"https://mp.weixin.qq.com/s?__biz=MzI2NDU4OTExOQ==&mid=2247695017&idx=1&sn=e37650a0f3334a69646fea9959c0297e","date":"2026-03-31 00:46:00","oneSentenceSummary":"本文探讨了 Harness Engineering 与规范驱动开发（SDD）的关系，强调在 AI 编程时代，工程纪律已从编写代码转向构建支撑 Agent 工作的规范与环境体系。","summary":"文章深入分析了由 OpenAI 和 Mitchell Hashimoto 提出的 Harness Engineering（支撑体系工程）概念，并探讨了其与规范驱动开发（SDD）的协同关系。作者指出，Harness Engineering 并非让规范变得多余，而是作为放大器，使结构化 Spec（规范）的重要性愈发凸显。在 AI 辅助编程的新范式下，工程纪律正从「写好代码」转向「构建好让 Agent 工作的脚手架（scaffolding）」。\n\n文章详细阐述了 Spec 在 Harness 体系中的三大核心角色：作为 Agent 推理的地图实现渐进式披露、提供 linter 无法覆盖的语义约束基础、以及作为反馈回路的正确性判据。通过 SDD 实践，开发者可以将模糊意图转化为结构化资产，消灭由于 Agent 猜测导致的返工成本。最后，作者提出了四项关键启示：人类注意力应从代码审查转向规范审查、区分执行与语义约束、建立规范漂移检测机制，以及在遇到问题时优先追问 AI 能力的缺失而非人类的努力程度。","archive_path":"data/articles/2026/03/RAW_67829792.json","topicTag":"ai-llm","category":"Programming_Technology","sourceName":"腾讯云开发者","resourceType":"ARTICLE","readTime":32,"score":91},{"id":"RAW_5ba4cd12","title":"CoPaw 深度解析：源码架构和功能实践","link":"https://mp.weixin.qq.com/s?__biz=MzIzOTU0NTQ0MA==&mid=2247559269&idx=1&sn=a87c6b0f00c2ccee4a25901df995c65b","date":"2026-03-31 00:30:00","oneSentenceSummary":"本文深入解析了基于 AgentScope 框架的开源桌面 Agent 工具 CoPaw 的技术架构、核心模块及部署实践。","summary":"文章对通义实验室发布的开源 Agent 工具 CoPaw 进行了全方位的技术拆解。首先详细介绍了 Agent Skill 这一标准化流程协议，阐述了其作为 LLM 和 Tool 之上第三层技术架构的核心作用。随后，文章深入剖析了 CoPaw 的八大技术模块，包括核心 Agent 类、可扩展的 Skills 系统、支持多协议的 MCP 客户端、具备动态聚合能力的记忆管理组件、支持云端与本地双部署的模型供应层、集成主流社交平台的 Channels 消息平台、任务执行工作流以及创新的 Cron Jobs 定时任务系统。最后，文章提供了详细的本地环境与阿里云 ACS 云端环境的部署指南及功能实践案例。","archive_path":"data/articles/2026/03/RAW_5ba4cd12.json","topicTag":"ai-llm","category":"Programming_Technology","sourceName":"阿里云开发者","resourceType":"ARTICLE","readTime":30,"score":90},{"id":"RAW_5ae30e5a","title":"Discord 开源 Osprey 安全规则引擎，每秒可处理 230 万条规则","link":"https://www.infoq.com/news/2026/03/discord-osprey/?utm_campaign=infoq_content&utm_source=infoq&utm_medium=feed&utm_term=global","date":"2026-03-31 00:11:00","oneSentenceSummary":"Discord 开源了 Osprey，这是一个高性能事件流决策引擎，利用 Rust 和 Python 的多语言架构，每秒可处理 230 万条规则。","summary":"Discord 已将 Osprey 作为开源项目发布，为工程社区提供了其用于实时威胁检测和自动响应的内部引擎。该系统专为处理海量规模而构建，每天评估 4 亿次操作。其架构特点是采用 Rust 协调器进行高并发流量管理，并使用无状态 Python 工作节点进行规则评估。规则使用 SML 编写，这是一种类似 Python 的 DSL，既确保了分析师的易用性，又允许工程师通过 Python UDF 扩展功能。随着 Bluesky 和 Matrix.org 的早期采用，Osprey 通过分离数据平面（Rust）和控制平面（Python），展示了一种高吞吐量系统的稳健模式。","archive_path":"data/articles/2026/03/RAW_5ae30e5a.json","topicTag":"other","category":"Programming_Technology","sourceName":"InfoQ","resourceType":"ARTICLE","readTime":3,"score":90},{"id":"RAW_86f36b4f","title":"如何在 React 中设计类型安全、懒加载且安全的插件架构","link":"https://www.freecodecamp.org/news/how-to-design-a-type-safe-lazy-and-secure-plugin-architecture-in-react/","date":"2026-03-30 18:06:36","archive_path":"data/articles/2026/03/RAW_86f36b4f.json","topicTag":"frontend-fullstack","category":"Programming_Technology","sourceName":"freeCodeCamp.org","resourceType":"ARTICLE","readTime":13,"score":90},{"id":"RAW_0df9b7df","title":"通过智能体、沙盒与人类协作，将 Turborepo 速度提升 96% - Vercel","link":"https://vercel.com/blog/ma