范式转变与实战深度解析","link":"https://mp.weixin.qq.com/s?__biz=MzIzOTU0NTQ0MA==&mid=2247559249&idx=1&sn=7cda1453a5f7f51c39f43b76027696a1","date":"2026-03-30 00:31:00","archive_path":"data/articles/2026/03/RAW_3aee2f2b.json","topicTag":"ai-llm","category":"Programming_Technology","sourceName":"阿里云开发者","resourceType":"ARTICLE","readTime":61,"score":90},{"id":"RAW_dd5cb7ce","title":"Midjourney 工程师发布开源库 Pretext，旨在革新网页设计","link":"https://venturebeat.com/technology/midjourney-engineer-debuts-new-vibe-coded-open-source-standard-pretext-to","date":"2026-03-30 23:58:37","oneSentenceSummary":"Cheng Lou 推出的全新开源库 Pretext 通过将文本布局与 DOM 解耦，利用两阶段执行模型实现高性能、可编程的文本渲染，从而革新了网页设计。","summary":"Pretext 是一个 15KB 的 TypeScript 库，它通过“准备（prepare）”和“布局（layout）”的两阶段执行模型，绕过了浏览器 DOM 重排（reflow）的瓶颈。通过利用 Canvas 字体度量和纯算术运算，它实现了 300-600 倍的性能提升，使得以往无法实现的流畅、交互式文本布局成为可能。Pretext 由 Cheng Lou 利用 AI 辅助编程开发，将文本视为一种可编程的媒介而非静态文档，为生成式 UI（Generative UI）、高频数据仪表盘和复杂的编辑设计提供了巨大潜力。虽然它引入了需要更多工程维护的“胖客户端”权衡，但它代表了 Web 架构的一次基础性转变。","archive_path":"data/articles/2026/03/RAW_dd5cb7ce.json","topicTag":"frontend-fullstack","category":"Business_Tech","sourceName":"VentureBeat","resourceType":"ARTICLE","readTime":8,"score":92},{"id":"RAW_15d5fd73","title":"RSAC 2026 发布了五个智能体身份框架，却留下了三个关键漏洞","link":"https://venturebeat.com/security/rsac-2026-agent-identity-frameworks-three-gaps","date":"2026-03-30 18:57:45","archive_path":"data/articles/2026/03/RAW_15d5fd73.json","topicTag":"ai-llm","category":"Business_Tech","sourceName":"VentureBeat","resourceType":"ARTICLE","readTime":8,"score":88},{"id":"RAW_febd5a6b","title":"三大模态模型全部登顶后，昆仑万维正式披露了 2026 年 AGI 战略","link":"https://mp.weixin.qq.com/s?__biz=Mzg5NTc0MjgwMw==&mid=2247523585&idx=1&sn=c196afdf81777bba739e5601873184e2","date":"2026-03-30 10:13:00","archive_path":"data/articles/2026/03/RAW_febd5a6b.json","topicTag":"other","category":"Business_Tech","sourceName":"Founder Park","resourceType":"ARTICLE","readTime":25,"score":87},{"id":"RAW_57aa8c54","title":"DeepSeek 修复故障，此前“已读不回”上热搜","link":"https://mp.weixin.qq.com/s?__biz=Mjc1NjM3MjY2MA==&mid=2691566451&idx=1&sn=3044691a08a78ea6ba93ac1fa2542b76","date":"2026-03-30 03:28:00","archive_path":"data/articles/2026/03/RAW_57aa8c54.json","topicTag":"ai-llm","category":"Business_Tech","sourceName":"腾讯科技","resourceType":"ARTICLE","readTime":5,"score":83},{"id":"RAW_44841a12","title":"深入揭秘那家兜售“无脑人类克隆体”的隐形初创公司","link":"https://www.technologyreview.com/2026/03/30/1134780/r3-bio-brainless-human-clones-full-body-replacement-john-schloendorn-aging-longevity/","date":"2026-03-30 01:26:49","archive_path":"data/articles/2026/03/RAW_44841a12.json","topicTag":"other","category":"Business_Tech","sourceName":"MIT Technology Review","resourceType":"ARTICLE","readTime":20,"score":89},{"id":"RAW_a31eadc","title":"Vol.110｜养虾时代，OpenClaw 让打工人何去何从？","link":"https://www.xiaoyuzhoufm.com/episode/69ca3e32b977fb2c47a0457d","date":"2026-03-31 01:00:00","oneSentenceSummary":"对话 Seele AI 创始人王诗沐与 Junior.so CTO 宇豪，深度探讨 AI 数字员工在企业中的落地实操、定价逻辑及「Harness Engineering」带来的组织变革。","summary":"本期播客聚焦 AI Agent（数字员工）从技术概念向企业实战演进的过程。Seele AI 创始人王诗沐分享了其推动全员 AI 自动化的激进决策，强调创业公司应通过变革追赶 AI 潮流；Junior.so CTO 宇豪则详细解析了其「数字员工」产品的逻辑：具备独立身份、以劳动力而非工具定价（月费 2000 美金）。核心内容涵盖了 AI 友好的「Harness Engineering」环境构建、企业数据安全的分级治理（T0-T2 风险定义）、以及「Context not Control」的管理哲学。讨论指出，AI 将重塑软件开发的范式，使企业从传统的 Build 模式转向「养虾（培养 Agent）」模式，通过极低的验证成本实现爆发式业务增长。","archive_path":"data/articles/2026/03/RAW_a31eadc.json","topicTag":"ai-llm","category":"Business_Tech","sourceName":"开始连接LinkStart","resourceType":"PODCAST","readTime":6,"score":92},{"id":"RAW_2038663014098899416","title":"Claude Code 现已支持电脑操控 (Computer Use)","link":"https://x.com/claudeai/status/2038663014098899416","date":"2026-03-30 17:01:53","archive_path":"data/articles/2026/03/RAW_2038663014098899416.json","topicTag":"ai-llm","category":"Artificial_Intelligence","sourceName":"Claude(@claudeai)","resourceType":"TWITTER","readTime":1,"score":92},{"id":"RAW_2038636335272194241","title":"Qwen3.5-Omni 发布：原生全模态 AGI","link":"https://x.com/Alibaba_Q